 "BOTH slices of `:construction-governor` are implemented end-to-end
 in `src/construction`. (1) disaster/severe-weather SAFETY slice --
 Construction Advisor (LLM proposal-only) ⊣ Construction Governor
 (legal-basis/threshold/inspection/report hard-gates), per-jurisdiction
 legal-basis catalog (JPN/USA/DEU, `construction.facts`) with real
 official sources, and mail+phone (Resend+Twilio) alert dispatch
 (`construction.notify`); four actuation ops (`:actuation/dispatch-
